         .chi-card__title(style="font-weight:400"; "font-size: 1.1rem") Guidance for developers 
       .chi-card__caption
          ul.-text
            li Simplify forms for better browser compatibility.
            li Use labels for inputs, matching for and id  attributes.
            li Keep IDs unique and pair each form element with one label.
            li Mark required fields clearly (e.g., with an asterisk).
            li Use aria-describedby for error message accessibility.
            li if there's an error message tagged with <code>id="my-error-message"</code>, then the corresponding input must include aria-describedby="my-error-message". 
      
